# --- Binaries ---
# Only ignore 'gator' in the root directory to avoid matching 
# folders or files like 'internal/gator/logic.go'
/gator
/gator.exe

# --- SQLite (If applicable) ---
# If you ever test with local SQLite files in this folder
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal

# --- System Junk ---
# macOS creates these hidden files in folders you browse
.DS_Store
# Windows creates these for folder thumbnails
Thumbs.db

# --- IDEs ---
# If you use VS Code or GoLand, ignore their internal settings
.vscode/
.idea/